<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <meta name="description" content="Buat tiket pengaduan IT baru">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/flash') %>
  <div class="app-layout">
    <%- include('../partials/sidebar') %>
    <div class="main-content">
      <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
      <div class="page-content">

        <div class="action-bar">
          <div>
            <div class="action-bar-title"><i class="bi bi-plus-circle" style="color:var(--accent);"></i> Buat Tiket Baru</div>
            <div style="font-size:.8rem; color:var(--text-muted);">Laporkan masalah IT yang Anda hadapi</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/tickets" class="btn-secondary-custom">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Kembali
          </a>
        </div>

        <div style="max-width:720px;">
          <div class="card-custom">
            <div class="card-header-custom">
              <div class="card-title-custom">
                <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-plus"></i> Informasi Tiket
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body-custom">
              <form action="/tickets" method="POST" id="createTicketForm">

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="form-label-custom" for="title">
                    Judul Tiket <span style="color:var(--danger);">*</span>
                  </label>
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    id="title"
                    name="title"
                    class="form-control-custom"
                    placeholder="Contoh: Komputer tidak bisa menyala di meja 12"
                    required
                    maxlength="200"
                  >
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="form-label-custom" for="category_id">Kategori</label>
                  <select id="category_id" name="category_id" class="form-control-custom">
                    <option value="">-- Pilih Kategori --</option>
                    <% categories.forEach(cat => { %>
                    <option value="<%= cat.id %>"><%= cat.name %></option>
                    <% }) %>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="form-label-custom" for="description">
                    Deskripsi Masalah <span style="color:var(--danger);">*</span>
                  </label>
                  <textarea
                    id="description"
                    name="description"
                    class="form-control-custom"
                    placeholder="Jelaskan masalah secara detail: kapan terjadi, gejala yang muncul, langkah yang sudah dicoba..."
                    rows="5"
                    required
                  ></textarea>
                </div>

                <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:1.25rem;">
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-label-custom" for="location">Lokasi / Ruangan</label>
                    <input
                      type="text"
                      id="location"
                      name="location"
                      class="form-control-custom"
                      placeholder="Contoh: Ruang Finance Lt. 2"
                    >
                  </div>

                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-label-custom" for="priority">Prioritas</label>
                    <select id="priority" name="priority" class="form-control-custom">
                      <option value="low">Rendah</option>
                      <option value="medium" selected>Sedang</option>
                      <option value="high">Tinggi</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--border); padding-top:1.25rem; margin-top:.5rem; display:flex; gap:.75rem;">
                  <button type="submit" class="btn-primary-custom" id="submitBtn">
                    <i class="bi bi-send"></i> Kirim Tiket
                  </button>
                  <a href="/tickets" class="btn-secondary-custom">Batal</a>
                </div>

              </form>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Tips Card -->
          <div class="card-custom" style="margin-top:1.25rem; border-left:4px solid var(--accent);">
            <div class="card-body-custom" style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;">
              <div style="font-weight:600; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:.5rem;">
                <i class="bi bi-lightbulb"></i> Tips Pengisian
              </div>
              <ul style="font-size:.82rem; color:var(--text-muted); padding-left:1.25rem; margin:0;">
                <li>Beri judul yang jelas dan spesifik</li>
                <li>Sertakan lokasi agar teknisi bisa langsung menuju ke tempat Anda</li>
                <li>Jelaskan kapan masalah pertama kali terjadi</li>
                <li>Jika ada error message, sertakan teksnya</li>
                <li>Pilih prioritas yang sesuai: Tinggi untuk masalah yang menghambat pekerjaan</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
